results.occurrenceRemarks: My 2nd necropsy of a Grampus griseus! It is the only species in the genus Grampus.  Some characteristics Cleft melon,  2-7 pairs of teeth on the lower jaw only, deep divers, excessive scaring. Japan is the only country that still hunts and slaughters the entire pod. This Genus of dolphins is very close to my heart and one of my favorites! Being so close  and necropsying this animal is one that I will never forget!
